"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640137099,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"11DeEw6ifseIu7iDaBCnEim0Z5WVePBKlVJD0yFgt5U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x182FBCC1b1E6e708529AaE2fEe10fc13a77D31ab\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ntb98jTpwlLoD_BiLQbgV4cyCIS2DOk31oFSGaPEY4s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"72NkZvg2vwiSEz5EEo-BCDwl4ZC6afySmaCrgNkF01Q\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"jb6O-WmwHSERrOLvCHGgquAo-v1QXkBq3ek5xL6wv-rZxhVcmacHGBBfamNWD3VDD_q75qZtQwPoc8ScjS2vmQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x074bfb2a095e60ee1e58448a7278201a9b2a5464897713d0d370581907940c0344c18bd60749a31b092aa5fe8ffc347521f85c05611c00bbf9eea23077aa549b1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ntb98jTpwlLoD_BiLQbgV4cyCIS2DOk31oFSGaPEY4s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"72NkZvg2vwiSEz5EEo-BCDwl4ZC6afySmaCrgNkF01Q\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi